            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Max Sprecher</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#sprecherM" start="1330.225" end="x">And so, we were submitted to a strong isolation. We were unable to learn from the fellow prisoners in the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>, of whom there were at that time ten thousand, what may happen to us, will happen. We were cut off from the outside [world], cut off from inside, delivered for life and death to a professional criminal as <a class="term" href="#vothG_blockalteste">block-elder</a> and to a women merchant, a room elder, as his helper.</span>
        </li>
