            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Max Sprecher</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#sprecherM" start="2710.029" end="x">At that time we were there a few thousand prisoners. The <a class="placename" href="#vothC18" type="camp">Buna</a> Project, the project for manufacture of artificial rubber, was planned and constructed for a half a million workers, mostly prisoners-workers. Already at that time there were working together with the thousand of Jewish prisoner-workers also civilians assembled in various <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lagers</a> consisting of Italians, French, Poles, Ukranians, and Russians. The whole project was exactly . . . the whole project . . . the industrial project <a class="placename" href="#vothC18" type="camp">Buna</a> was . . .</span>
        </li>
