            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#sprecherM" start="2980.534" end="x">I was washing the clothes which were handed to me from the kettle. The clothing consisted . . . that what I was washing consistd of suits, striped and non-striped, clothing that was given after long intervals to the prisoners to change. And . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="3005.109" end="x">Go on . . .</span>
